data.title: Hill Country Lashes in Lakeway, TX
data.meta_description: Commitment to your lash beauty and health! Hill County Lashes offer styles ranging from natural to glamorous! Please contact me for more information.
data.text:
Classic Lash Extension Full Set

A beautiful way to enhance your lashes with a natural looking length and fullness.

All persons under the age of 18 must be accompanied by a parent or guardian. $150 · 1 hour 45 minutes

Lash Extension Consultation

Consultations are recommended for microblading and lash extension clients. This will allow me to check for allergies and give me the chance to appropriately address any concerns or questions you may have. Consults should be scheduled at least 24 hour before your full microblading or lash extension appointment.

Free · 20 minutes
